Direct Data for Snowflake

After you complete setup, CRM Analytics Direct Data for Snowflake lets you run queries on the dataset associated with the connection in real time. You can also build dashboard charts and tables based on the queries you run on Snowflake data.

To create live connections to Snowflake: Enable CRM Analytics Direct Data for external data sources
To explore data directly in Snowflake: Explore External Data Directly

Data stored in the Snowflake object opens in a lens, which you can interactively explore and visualize.
